OL,6,FChilling CCTV footage has been
OL,7,Freleased showing a man enter the home
OL,8,Fof his ex-partner and leave one minute
OL,9,Flater, having stabbed her multiple
OL,10,Ftimes in a jealous rage.
OL,12,FWilliam Finlay admitted murdering
OL,13,Fretired nurse Alyson Nelson in a
OL,14,F'premeditated and vicious' attack in
OL,15,Fthe mother-of-four's Whitehead home in
OL,16,FApril 2022.
OL,18,FThe 68-year-old, of Old Forde Gardens
OL,19,Fin Whitehead, was given a 20-year
OL,20,Fprison sentence on Thursday.
