OL,6,FAt the tariff hearing in Belfast Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Mr Justice O'Hara said Ms
OL,8,FNelson was a former nurse and that
OL,9,F"public service ran in her family".
OL,11,FHe said Finlay had met Ms Nelson
OL,12,Fonline in December 2018 and had later
OL,13,Fmoved in with her.
OL,15,FAfter their brief relationship ended,
OL,16,Fthere was ongoing limited contact
OL,17,Fbetween them and Ms Nelson had started
OL,18,Fa new relationship with another man.
