OL,6,FThe judge said CCTV captured Finlay
OL,7,Fgoing to her home on the night of
OL,8,FApril 16 2022, where he stabbed her a
OL,9,Fnumber of times in a "vicious,
OL,10,Funrelenting attack".
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Michelle Griffin
OL,13,Fhas welcomed the sentencing of William
OL,14,FFinlay for the murder of Alyson
OL,15,FNelson, describing it as the first for
OL,16,Fmurder aggravated by domestic abuse
OL,17,Fsince new legislation became law in
OL,18,F2022.
