OL,6,FSpeaking outside Belfast Crown Court,
OL,7,Fshe said: "Today he was told he will
OL,8,Fserve a minimum of 20 years in prison.
OL,10,F"Alyson Nelson, who was 64 years old,
OL,11,Fwas attacked by William Finlay on
OL,12,FSaturday, April 16, 2022. She was
OL,13,Fstabbed multiple times in her own home
OL,14,Fin the village of Whitehead. A place
OL,15,Fshe should have felt safe.
