OL,6,F"Alyson was a much-loved mother,
OL,7,Fgrandmother and sister. The entire
OL,8,Ffamily has suffered a huge loss made
OL,9,Fonly the more agonising by the cruel
OL,10,Fway in which her life was actually
OL,11,Ftaken.
OL,13,F"William Finlay and Alyson had
OL,14,Fpreviously been in a relationship
OL,15,Fwhich had ended over a year before the
OL,16,Ffatal stabbing even took place.
