OL,6,F"As a result, William Finlay is the
OL,7,Ffirst person in Northern Ireland to be
OL,8,Fconvicted and sentenced for murder
OL,9,Fwhich has been aggravated by domestic
OL,10,Fabuse under new legislation.
OL,12,F"I know that Alyson's loving family
OL,13,Fare heartbroken and my thoughts, and
OL,14,Fthe thoughts of our entire team,
OL,15,Fremain with them today."
